description:
The SDK exposes a method `updateMeasurementContext(<measurementId>, <context>)` that takes a `measurementId` string and `context` object as input. 
After executing the method, the measurement context is updated. 

The `context` object has the following properties:
```
{
    "context": {
        "activity": "sitting",
        "symptoms": ["fatigue"],
        "symptomSeverity": "2a"
    }
}
```
